dcterms:description: The dataset consists of births between 2002 and 2014, extracted from the Indonesian Family Life Survey (IFLS). It is used to evaluate the impact of a national health insurance programme on the probability of births being assisted by a health care professional.
dcterms:title: Indonesian Family Life Survey (IFLS)
